{"article_id":"CXlHsMwfTMfAjJ0R","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Bachmann ' s decision comes","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"as she faces a growing swirl of investigations .","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Bachmann 's fall","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"Rep. Michele Bachmann","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"( R-Minn. )","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"- the tea-party firebrand","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"facing investigations and a daunting reelection race -","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"abruptly announced on Wednesday morning","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that she will not seek reelection to a fifth term .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Her move marked a spectacular fall for a congresswoman with a bull ' s eye on her back every congressional cycle :","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Less than two years ago , she won the Iowa straw poll","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and was briefly regarded as a serious contender for the GOP presidential nomination .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Bachmann , 57 ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"who took office in 2007 ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"said in a video","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"posted on her website :","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"\" My good friends :","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"After a great deal of thought and deliberation , I have decided","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"next year","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"I will not seek a fifth congressional term","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"to represent the wonderful people of the Sixth District of Minnesota .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"After serious consideration , I am confident","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that this is the right decision . \"","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"With Bachmann ' s departure , the tea party ' s voice in Congress will dim .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"She is the movement ' s third big-name figure in recent months","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to leave Congress","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"- Jim DeMint of South Carolina resigned from the Senate in January","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to take over the Heritage Foundation .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"And in November , Florida Rep. Allen West , another conservative bomb thrower , lost reelection .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Ironically , the retirement may improve Republicans ' chances","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"of holding Minnesota ' s conservative 6th Congressional District ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"which broke for Mitt Romney by nearly 15 percentage points in 2012 .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Democrats had Bachmann at the top of their target list","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"after she barely survived reelection last year .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"The Democrat","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"who came close to defeating her ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Jim Graves , was gearing up for a rematch .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Bachmann ' s decision comes","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"as she faces a growing swirl of investigations into her campaign finances ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"with the The Federal Election Commission and the Office of Congressional Ethics opening investigations","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"into whether her campaign concealed payments to an Iowa state senator","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"who did work for her 2012 presidential bid .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Last week , the FBI reportedly joined the inquiry .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"In Graves , she was up against an opponent","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"who came within 5,000 votes","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"- or 1.2 percent points -","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"of unseating her last November .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Graves , a wealthy hotel company executive","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"who poured $ 250,000 of his own funds into the 2012 contest ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"released a poll last week","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"showing him with a narrow lead over the congresswoman .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"The Democratic Congressional Campaign Committee ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"which provided Graves with little help in 2012 ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"had indicated","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"that it planned to get behind the challenger aggressively in Round Two .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Though Bachmann would have had an enormous war chest ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"the defeat of West","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"- another tea party hero with a national following and big money -","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"showed","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that such figures are not invincible .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Potential Republican candidates for the seat include state Reps. Tim Sanders and Matt Dean , state Sen. Michelle Fischbach , and St . Cloud Mayor Dave Kleis .","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"In the video","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"released Wednesday morning ,","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Bachmann insisted","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that her decision","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"to not seek reelection","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"had nothing to do with the Graves challenge , nor from the investigations .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Bachmann aides have repeatedly said","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"the congresswoman has done nothing improper .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"\" Be assured :","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"My decision was not in any way influenced by any concerns","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"about my being reelected to Congress . ...","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"I have every confidence","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"if I ran ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"I would again defeat the individual","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"who I defeated last year ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"who recently announced","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"he is once again running .","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":157,"left":80,"right":156,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":80,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":2,"right":155,"relation":"o